    <h1>A quorum, not a chorus. <em>Twenty-five LLM analysts argue across six schools.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Quorai is a research sandbox for AI-driven investment analysis. Twenty-five language-model
      agents — investor personas paired with quant, sentiment, and valuation specialists — are
      sorted into six schools of thought. Each school weighs its members by conviction, not by
      headcount; when the schools disagree, the disagreement itself becomes the signal.
      Nothing is ever actually traded.
